如何看待其这一表态？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "据 CGTN，当地时间 9 月 10 日，拜登在越南进行国事访问时发表了演讲。在谈到中国时他表示，自己很真诚地想处理好与中国的关系，不希望与中国脱钩。他不会向中国出售制造核武器的材料，但也并不想伤害中国。拜登再次表示不愿与中国脱钩 | 界面新闻 · 快讯"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-f8f20a48b7f2e3f249412f7b3c3abf07_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "259 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/621481155"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIr5Ktjduc1/wKEAMaCTEwMDM4NjY1NSCN7vqnBjAAOMgBQANyCTYyMTQ4MTE1NXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "4_1694437732.948697", "card_id": "EV_12220913", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 0}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么「秀才」和「一笑倾城」能成为治愈大爷大妈的新生代顶流？为何更容易俘获中老年人的心？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-4d3ecb6a6b411a946ba7c31e697b6a5e_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "187 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/theater/10156"}, "tag_area": {"normal_url": "", "night_url": "", "width": 0, "height": 0}}, "attached_info": "ClgIr5Ktjduc1/wKEBgaBDc2NDggytn6pwZABHIIMTIyMjA5MTN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZMoBI2h0dHBzOi8vd3d3LnpoaWh1LmNvbS90aGVhdGVyLzEwMTU2"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "5_1694437732.948718", "card_id": "Q_621474899", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 30}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "9  月 11 日人民币止跌回升，人民币中间价调升 2 基点报 7.2148，人民币未来走势如何？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "9 月 11 日，人民银行授权中国外汇交易中心公布，2023 年 9 月 11 日银行间外汇市场人民币汇率中间价为：1 美元对人民币 7.2148 元，前一交易日中间价报 7.2150 元，单日调升 2 基点。 在前一交易